          <tr><td>Main control board replacement</td><td>$650–$1,200</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Multi-component service (board + motor + hinge)</td><td>$900–$1,600</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p class="small">
        Most Vulcan service calls land $300–$750 parts-and-labor. See the product-specific pages (Vulcan fryer above;
        oven and range coming soon) for model-level pricing detail. Full cross-brand context at our <a href="/price-list/commercial-fryer-repair-cost/">commercial
        fryer repair cost guide</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
